s://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Di%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjuk7qr9O_jAhVNA4gKHWFqA3oQzPwBegQIARAC%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.washingtonpost.com%252Ftechnology%252F2019%252F06%252F10%252Fyour-face-is-now-your-boarding-pass-thats-problem%252F%26psig%3DAOvVaw0ESOWjJVtA4Ck6xFaRNIvO%26ust%3D1565238072056708&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apLzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=66e88439\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;source=web&amp;cd=&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjuk7qr9O_jAhVNA4gKHWFqA3oQzPwBegQIARAC&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2Fyour-face-is-now-your-boarding-pass-thats-problem%2F&amp;psig=AOvVaw0ESOWjJVtA4Ck6xFaRNIvO&amp;ust=1565238072056708</a><br />\n<br />\n補充資料 from Washington post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82131aeba0432e263c9dac62ba70c9d319daa874","tid":1426756,"uid":278667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"推啊~~~~"},{"pid":"63e8b93819497c17e8c0067b0422cfb8ef020b1b","tid":1426756,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"朋友幫手加咗英文版，跪求全能連登仔翻譯日文韓文，加圖片整成傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為何要小心人面識別系統？<br />\nWhy you should be worried about facial recognition at Hong King Airport?<br />\n- 人面是獨一無二的生物特徵，屬於重要個人資料。不當使用會引致難以預計的損失。<br />\nYour facial features are identical and should be treated as an important personal information, the mishandling of which may lead to unpredictable loss of your interest. <br />\n- 香港多地安裝有人面識別功能的監控鏡頭。你在香港的行蹤及有電子紀錄的行為，都可經人面識別系統進行監控，例如乘搭地鐵、信用卡消費等。<br />\nCameras that are able to perform facial recognition have been installed on the streets and in metro stations of chinese-ruled Hong Kong. Your activities could be under surveillance. <br />\n- 中國政府運用人面識別系統大規模監控國民，<br />\n入境的境外人士同樣受相關法律規管。<br />\nChina has an obnoxious record of human rights violation by putting citizens under surveillance programme. Foreigners visiting China are also subject to the legislations where applicable. <br />\n<br />\n你可以怎樣做？<br />\nWhat you can do to protect your privacy <br />\n- 根據機場自助保安閘口－私隱政策聲明，你有權拒絕機場收集你的人面特徵。請向職員表明要求，他會安排輔助通道。此要求不會影響你的行程。<br />\nWith reference to Airport e-Security Gates &ndash; Privacy Policy Statement, you have the right to refuse the collection of your personal data. In such case please make a request to the staff at the departure gate. Assisted channels shall be provided to you without taking photo of your face. This request will not interfere your journey. <br />\n- 目前只有一號客運大樓設有人面識別系統，你可以到二號客運大樓離境，同樣可以到達所有登機閘口。<br />\nAt the moment, facial recognition cameras are set up at Terminal 1 only. You can make use of the departure gate at Terminal 2 to avoid taking photo of your face. All boarding gates are accessible from Terminal 2.<br />\n- 如果你已經被拍攝照片，你有權要求刪除資料。請向機場識員或電郵機場管理局提出要求。<br />\nIf unfortunately photos of your face have been taken, you are still entitled to request deletion of your personal data. Please make a request to the staff, or email to the Airport Authority."},{"pid":"17dc634017b0d964a2eb521639e601ba443c03f7","tid":1426756,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:00:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"19f5788a32ef46d24896d4d2f5606039dbedcd5e","tid":1426756,"uid":278667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"e468bcc19edea1046fa524cc7d06b32c882a8b69","tid":1426756,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:04:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d1d5e5e2b9d382dc8cdfdadd6a73b12152f1eb","tid":1426756,"uid":269622